Baby Go by Treasure Marie Denise Jackson & GOD A.K.A. Jesus Christ

https://textadventures.co.uk/games/view/k9hi58vspku0_iswufc22w/baby-go

This is a prequal to _"Go, Baby Go!"_ Which is still in the works.

This is the story of the twins that took care of _Golly Polly & Polly Sye_ & their struggle to survive in a world that never wanted them but created them regardless & never valued them.
